window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A man who commands dragons rises. The people call him a prophet, a savior...the one who will free them from the tyranny of the wizard class.&nbsp;</b></p> <p><b>They do not comprehend the threat he presents.</b></p> <p>The dragon priest rages across the land. Cities and rulers are helpless against his might.&nbsp;</p> <p>A pair of heroes embark on a dangerous quest, seeking a lost object of power. Without it, the dragon priest and his army will destroy the world.</p> <p>An army of metal golems invades another wizardom. These magic-powered automatons are the weapon of the last wizard lord - a madman who desires to rule the world. Despite his might, betrayal might be his most useful tool.</p> <p><b><i>Shadow of a Dragon Priest</i></b><b> continues the Fall of Wizardoms Saga, an epic fantasy adventure rife with action, intrigue, and witty banter.</b></p> <p><b>Narrated in grand fashion by the vaunted talent, Travis Baldree.</b></p>"; 
